         <section>
            <title>Testing</title>
            <p>We have two test routines for Inari Sámi:</p>
            <ol>
               <li>In gt/smn/testing: <code>make n-paradigm WORD=testword</code></li>
               <li>In gt/: <code>make fsttest GTLANG=smn</code></li>
            </ol>
            <p>The first routine runs against noun-codes.txt.</p>
            <p>The second routine uses the file <a
            href="https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/gt/smn/testing/smn-tests.yaml">smn/testing/smn-tests.yaml</a>.
            Feel free to add paradigms.</p>
